metadata.name: Systems of Now Token  #1/44
metadata.description:
SYSTEMS OF NOW TOKEN is collaged edition of 44 pieces made using a variety of AI techniques.  
The tokens can be used to claim an Ordinals Systems of Now generative art project . 
Each of the 44 NFT tokens on this Manifold contract exist to represent a unique generative art piece to be inscribed onto the Bitcoin blockchain, made via a p5.JS program together with GPT3 during January 2023 .  
The Generative pieces will be sent to each holder via applicable Ordinal wallet once the claim is finished.  
Ethereum tokens on this Manifold contract will never be burned.
